{"date":"2009-05-24","platform":"OVA","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/39/66/37874_qB06C.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/39/66/37874_qB06C.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/39/66/37874_qB06C.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/39/66/37874_qB06C.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/39/66/37874_qB06C.jpg"},"summary":"在光坂高中空无一人的教室内，藤林椋终于鼓起勇气向被人当作不良少年的冈崎朋也表白。幸运的是，她的爱意没有落于虚空，得到了冈崎热情而肯定的回应。两人自此开始交往，望着沉浸在幸福中的妹妹，藤林杏心中自是无法道出的复杂感受。某个明媚的假日，冈崎和杏在公园不期而遇。杏半开玩笑地教冈崎把自己当作椋练习接吻，谁知这一幕却被同学看见，第二天便在学校内传得风言风语。为了消除谣言，杏甚至假装和春原阳平交往。甜蜜又青涩的学生时代，说不清道不明的爱恋情怀……","name":"CLANNAD 〜AFTER STORY〜もうひとつの世界 杏編","name_cn":"CLANNAD ～AFTER STORY～另一个世界 杏篇","tags":[{"name":"京阿尼","count":1971,"total_cont":0},{"name":"Clannad","count":1699,"total_cont":0},{"name":"OVA","count":1675,"total_cont":0},{"name":"key","count":1409,"total_cont":0},{"name":"GAL改","count":937,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2009","count":721,"total_cont":0},{"name":"杏篇","count":719,"total_cont":0},{"name":"麻枝准","count":710,"total_cont":0},{"name":"校园","count":687,"total_cont":0},{"name":"催泪","count":634,"total_cont":0},{"name":"治愈","count":483,"total_cont":0},{"name":"游戏改","count":419,"total_cont":0},{"name":"恋爱","count":355,"total_cont":0},{"name":"短发杏","count":278,"total_cont":0},{"name":"石原立也","count":224,"total_cont":0},{"name":"京都动画","count":144,"total_cont":0},{"name":"京都","count":90,"total_cont":0},{"name":"日本","count":88,"total_cont":0},{"name":"STORY～もうひとつの世界","count":46,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2009年5月","count":45,"total_cont":0},{"name":"京都アニメーション","count":42,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2009年","count":37,"total_cont":0},{"name":"日常","count":22,"total_cont":0},{"name":"神作","count":21,"total_cont":0},{"name":"人生","count":18,"total_cont":0},{"name":"番外","count":18,"total_cont":0},{"name":"TV","count":16,"total_cont":0},{"name":"中村悠一","count":14,"total_cont":0},{"name":"藤林杏","count":11,"total_cont":0},{"name":"爱情","count":10,"total_cont":0}],"infobox":[{